behavior find_pajamas_2039_around_bed_264(pajamas:item):
    goal: not unknown(pajamas)
    body:
        assert is_pajamas(pajamas)
        bind bed_instance:item where:
            is_bed(bed_instance) and id[bed_instance]==264
        achieve close_char(char,bed_instance)
        if can_open(bed_instance):
            achieve_once open(bed_instance)
            exp(pajamas,bed_instance)
        else:
            exp(pajamas,bed_instance)
    eff:
        unknown[pajamas]=False
        close[pajamas,bed_instance]=True
        close[bed_instance,pajamas]=True

#goal_representation
 
behavior place_clothes_in_machine(clothes:item, machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(machine) # Ensure the washing machine is closed
        achieve is_on(machine) # Ensure the washing machine is turned on

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and dirty(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

behavior place_clothes_in_machine(clothes:item, machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(machine) # Ensure the washing machine is closed
        achieve is_on(machine) # Ensure the washing machine is turned on

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and dirty(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the operational washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

behavior find_basket_for_clothes_2040_around_bed_264(basket_for_clothes:item):
    goal: not unknown(basket_for_clothes)
    body:
        assert is_basket_for_clothes(basket_for_clothes)
        bind bed_instance:item where:
            is_bed(bed_instance) and id[bed_instance]==264
        achieve close_char(char,bed_instance)
        if can_open(bed_instance):
            achieve_once open(bed_instance)
            exp(basket_for_clothes,bed_instance)
        else:
            exp(basket_for_clothes,bed_instance)
    eff:
        unknown[basket_for_clothes]=False
        close[basket_for_clothes,bed_instance]=True
        close[bed_instance,basket_for_clothes]=True

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket: item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine which is plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Move all clothes from the basket to the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket) # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all the clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select a washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) 
        # Ensure the washing machine door is closed

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is turned on to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket_for_clothes: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket_for_clothes)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine, ensuring it is plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket_for_clothes):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket for clothes into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) 
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is closed before starting
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and turned on
        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start the washing cycle

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the turned on washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
                # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

behavior load_clothes(clothing: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothing, washing_machine)
        # Load the clothing item into the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)  # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine)
        # Select the pluggedin washing machine

        foreach clothing: item:
            if is_clothes(clothing) and inside(clothing, basket):
                load_clothes(clothing, washing_machine)
                # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_and_start_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place clothes inside the washing machine
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket_for_clothes: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket_for_clothes)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select a washing machine
        
        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket_for_clothes):
                load_and_start_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            foreach clothes: item:
                if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                    achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
                    # Ensure all clothes from the basket are placed inside the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure all clothes are placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start the wash cycle

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the prepared washing machine, which is plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine to wash the clothes

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the door of the washing machine

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start the washing cycle

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine]==2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes in the basket into the washing machine
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is already plugged in

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensures the clothes are placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensures the washing machine is closed before starting
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select a basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select a pluggedin and turnedon washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
def has_dirty_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are dirty clothes in the specified basket
    symbol has_dirty_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and dirty(c) and inside(c, basket)
    return has_dirty_clothes

behavior load_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is already turned on
        
        if has_dirty_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            foreach c: item:
                # Load all dirty clothes from the basket into the washing machine
                if is_clothes(c) and dirty(c) and inside(c, basket):
                    load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
            start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in a specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve has_water(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is filled with water
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine thats plugged in and turned on

        if exists clothes: item : is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
            foreach clothes: item:
                if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                    place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
            start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothes are inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior load_clothes(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        
        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes(clothes, washing_machine)
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

        achieve close_char(char,bed_instance)
        if can_open(bed_instance):
            achieve_once open(bed_instance)
            exp(clothes_underwear,bed_instance)
        else:
            exp(clothes_underwear,bed_instance)
    eff:
        unknown[clothes_underwear]=False
        close[clothes_underwear,bed_instance]=True
        close[bed_instance,clothes_underwear]=True

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select a washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, machine)
        # Ensure that the clothes are placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(machine) 
        # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(machine) 
        # Ensure the washing machine is turned on

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the clothes basket

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine]==2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

behavior find_clothes_scarf_2079_around_bed_264(clothes_scarf:item):
    goal: not unknown(clothes_scarf)
    body:
        assert is_clothes_scarf(clothes_scarf)
        bind bed_instance:item where:
            is_bed(bed_instance) and id[bed_instance]==264
        achieve close_char(char,bed_instance)
        if can_open(bed_instance):
            achieve_once open(bed_instance)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is already plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and dirty(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket: item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in a specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if not has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            observe(basket, "Check if there are clothes in the basket")
        
        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place all clothes from the basket into the washing machine


#goal_representation_end

        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to wash the clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
def is_washing_machine_loaded(washing_machine:item):
    # Determine whether the washing machine is loaded with clothes
    symbol has_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and inside(c, washing_machine)
    return has_clothes

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if not is_washing_machine_loaded(washing_machine):
            foreach clothes: item:
                if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                    load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
def contains_dirty_clothes(basket:item):
    # Function to check if the basket contains dirty clothes
    symbol has_dirty_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket) and dirty(c)
    return has_dirty_clothes

behavior load_washing_machine_with_clothes(washing_machine:item, basket:item):
    body:
        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
                # Place each piece of clothing from the basket into the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is closed

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing the clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if contains_dirty_clothes(basket):
            load_washing_machine_with_clothes(washing_machine, basket)
            start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
            # Start the washing sequence if dirty clothes are present


#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Put the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start the washing process

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        foreach c: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_in_washing_machine(washing_machine:item, clothes_basket:item):
    body:
        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, clothes_basket):
                achieve inside(c, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is closed before starting
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind clothes_basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(clothes_basket)
        # Select the clothes basket

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        load_clothes_in_washing_machine(washing_machine, clothes_basket)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine once the clothes are inside
        achieve has_water(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine has water
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket_for_clothes: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket_for_clothes)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket_for_clothes):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        assert is_clothes(clothes)
        # Ensure the item is clothing
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine
        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior load_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine] == 2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            foreach c: item:
                if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                    load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
            # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine after loading clothes

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) 
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start the washing process

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure all clothes from the basket are inside the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
def is_washing_machine_ready(washing_machine: item):
    # Determine if the washing machine is ready to use
    return is_on(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine)

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place each item of clothing inside the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and is_washing_machine_ready(washing_machine)
        # Select a readytouse washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket of clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine which is already turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
def contains_clothes(basket: item):
    # Check if a basket contains clothes
    symbol contains_clothes = exists clothes: item : is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket)
    return contains_clothes

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket_for_clothes: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket_for_clothes)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if not contains_clothes(basket_for_clothes):
            observe(basket_for_clothes, "Check if there are clothes in the basket")

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket_for_clothes):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing process

#goal_representation_end

        # Ensure all clothes are placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine]==2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(machine)
        achieve is_on(machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve has_water(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket_for_clothes: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket_for_clothes)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the plugged and switched on washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket_for_clothes):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_to_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure all the clothes are inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_to_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine]==2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes(clothes, washing_machine)
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothing item is placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine door is closed

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn the washing machine on to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothes are inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing process

#goal_representation_end

    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Place all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                put_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
                
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is turned on

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the clothes basket

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine]==2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing process

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Put clothes inside the washing machine

behavior close_washing_machine_door(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Identify the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine] == 2041
        # Identify the specific washing machine with ID 2041
        
        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        close_washing_machine_door(washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in a specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior wash_clothes(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure clothes are placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            bind washing_machine: item where:
                is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
            # Select the washing machine

            foreach clothes: item:
                if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                    wash_clothes(clothes, washing_machine)
            start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing the clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Bind the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine] == 2041
        # Bind the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_inside_basket(basket: item):
    # Determine whether there are clothes inside the basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if has_clothes_inside_basket(basket):
            foreach c: item:
            # Load all clothes from the basket to the washing machine
                if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                    load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
            start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place clothes inside the washing machine

behavior turn_on_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve has_water(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine has water
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        
        turn_on_washing_machine(washing_machine)


#goal_representation_end

behavior find_pajamas_2039_around_bed_264(pajamas:item):
    goal: not unknown(pajamas)
    body:
        assert is_pajamas(pajamas)
        bind bed_instance:item where:
            is_bed(bed_instance) and id[bed_instance]==264

        if can_open(bed_instance):

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) 
        # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select a washing machine
        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve has_water(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine has water to wash clothes
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start the washing process

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):

        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)

                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place each item of clothing inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start the cycle

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and switched on

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve has_water(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine has water
        
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is closed
        
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select a washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
                
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes(washing_machine:item, basket:item):
    body:
        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                achieve inside(c, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        load_clothes(washing_machine, basket)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

        else:
            exp(clothes_scarf,bed_instance)
    eff:
        unknown[clothes_scarf]=False

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)

        # Select the washing machine that is already plugged in and on

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and dirty(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select an on and plugged washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
                # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if the basket contains clothes
    symbol has_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            # If the basket contains clothes, proceed to wash them
            foreach c: item:
                if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                    achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
            # Place all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

            achieve closed(washing_machine)
            # Ensure the washing machine door is closed

            achieve is_on(washing_machine)
            # Ensure the washing machine is turned on to start washing

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothes are inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is closed

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket of clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine] == 2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

        close[bed_instance,clothes_underwear]=True
    

#exp_behavior_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior fill_washing_machine_with_clothes(clothes_basket:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, clothes_basket):
                achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
                # Ensure all clothes from the basket are put into the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Once the clothes are loaded, close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind clothes_basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(clothes_basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Make sure the washing machine is selected and is on

        fill_washing_machine_with_clothes(clothes_basket, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is on
        
        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all dirty clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):

    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket containing clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the already switched on and plugged in washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

            exp(clothes_underwear,bed_instance)
    eff:

        close[clothes_underwear,bed_instance]=True

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is turned on and plugged in

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and dirty(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) 
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) 

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
        # Load all dirty clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) 
        # Start the washing process
#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)  # Ensure the washing machine is closed
        achieve has_water(washing_machine)  # Ensure the washing machine has water
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)  # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
                # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
                
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)  # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the clothes basket

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior transfer_clothes_to_washer(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine] == 2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                transfer_clothes_to_washer(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior switch_on_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve plugged(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
                # Place each piece of clothing from the basket into the washing machine
        
        switch_on_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is plugged in and turned on

behavior start_washing_machine(machine:item):

        achieve closed(machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):

        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
            # Select the washing machine
        
        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
                # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is turned on

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine
