#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(cloth: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(cloth, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on and start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine which is plugged in and turned on
        
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
            
        foreach cloth: item:
            if is_clothes(cloth) and inside(cloth, basket):
                load_washing_machine(cloth, washing_machine)
                # Load each piece of clothing from the basket into the washing machine

        close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Close and start the washing machine after loading all the clothes

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation

def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior load_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place clothes inside the washing machine

behavior close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select a washing machine

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            foreach clothes: item:
                if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                    load_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
            close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothes are placed inside the washing machine

behavior turn_on_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is turned on

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that has already been turned on

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        turn_on_washing_machine(washing_machine) 
        # Start the washing machine if not already on

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine, ensuring it is plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

        else:
            exp(clothes_shirt,bed_instance)
    eff:
        unknown[clothes_shirt]=False
        close[clothes_shirt,bed_instance]=True
        close[bed_instance,clothes_shirt]=True

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket)
    return has_clothes

def is_basket_at_washing_machine(basket:item, washing_machine:item):
    # Checks if the basket is close to the washing machine
    symbol close_basket=close(basket, washing_machine)
    return close_basket

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure clothes are placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine]==2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        assert is_basket_at_washing_machine(basket, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the basket is close to the washing machine

        if not has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            observe(basket,"Check is there any clothes in the basket")

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select a washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve has_water(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine has water
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine] == 2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            foreach c: item:
                if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                    load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
            start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        else:
            foreach basket: item:
                if is_basket_for_clothes(basket) and not visited(basket):
                    observe(basket,"Check if there are clothes in the basket")

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine] == 2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach c: item:
        # Load all clothes items from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):

        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is turned on to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                # Load each clothing item from the basket into the washing machine
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine after loading all clothes

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket: item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            # If there are clothes in the basket, transfer them into the washing machine
            foreach o: item:
                if is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket):
                    achieve inside(o, washing_machine)
        else:
            # If no clothes are found in the basket, observe to find clothes and transfer them into the washing machine
            observe(basket, "Check if there are clothes in the basket")
            foreach o: item:
                if is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket):
                    achieve inside(o, washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) 
        # Ensure the washing machine door is closed

        achieve is_on(washing_machine) 
        # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine which is already plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

behavior put_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is already plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Place all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                put_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothes are placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is started

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine for use

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
                # Place each piece of clothing from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load each piece of clothing inside the washing machine

behavior close_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is closed before starting

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is turned on to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and switched on

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes inside the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        close_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing cycle

#goal_representation_end

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine based on available knowledge

        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine to wash the clothes

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothing:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothing, washing_machine)

def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        assert has_clothes_in_basket(basket)

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
            # The washing machine used has already been plugged and turned on in previous actions
        
        foreach clothing: item:
            if is_clothes(clothing) and inside(clothing, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothing, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine with all collected clothes inside

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

def clothes_in_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes already inside the washing machine
    symbol clothes_in_machine=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, washing_machine)
    return clothes_in_machine

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine
        
behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is turned on to start the washing process

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if not clothes_in_washing_machine(washing_machine):
            # If there are no clothes already in the washing machine, load them from the basket
            foreach clothes: item:
                if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                    load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothes are inside the washing machine

behavior close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is already on
        
        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        
        close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Close and start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothes are inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket containing the clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select an already plugged in and turned on washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing process

behavior load_washing_machine(item:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(item, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the item (clothes) is inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        foreach item: item:
            if is_clothes(item) and inside(item, basket):
                load_washing_machine(item, washing_machine)
                # Load clothes from the basket to the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine to wash clothes

#goal_representation
 
behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve has_water(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine has water
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is turned on to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior load_clothes(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure each clothing item is placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Make sure the washing machine is closed before starting
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to wash the clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the clothes basket

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is already plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine to wash the clothes

#goal_representation_end

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine]==2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_in_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine to use

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_clothes_in_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
                # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
      
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and dirty(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_clothes_into_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine] == 2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041
        
        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            # If the basket has clothes, process them for washing
            foreach c: item:
                if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                    achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
            # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            
            achieve is_on(washing_machine)
            # Ensure the washing machine is turned on


#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine
#goal_representation_end

behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothing items inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine door is closed

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine] == 2041
        # Select the washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)  # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)   # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine is closed before starting
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the laundry basket

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(basket:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        foreach clothing: item:
            if is_clothes(clothing) and inside(clothing, basket):
                achieve inside(clothing, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        
        load_clothes_into_washing_machine(basket, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in a specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists c: item : is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(cloth:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(cloth, washing_machine)
        # Place the cloth inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            foreach c: item:
                if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                    load_clothes_into_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
            start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        else:
            observe(basket, "Check if there are any clothes in the basket")

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve has_water(washing_machine) 
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(item:item, machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(item, machine)
        # Place the item inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is closed before starting

        achieve has_water(machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine has water

        achieve is_on(machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to start washing the clothes

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine to start washing

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is plugged and turned on

        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
                # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

        achieve closed(washing_machine)

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)

behavior load_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothes are inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and id[washing_machine]==2041
        # Select washing machine with ID 2041

        foreach c: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Identify the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Identify the washing machine that is plugged in and switched on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_into_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Load each piece of clothing from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, machine)
        # Ensures clothes are inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(machine)
        # Ensures the washing machine is closed

        achieve has_water(machine)
        # Ensures the washing machine has water

        achieve is_on(machine)
        # Ensures the washing machine is turned on

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the clothes basket

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
                # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
behavior place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine that is turned on

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                place_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the item is placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is turned on

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine, ensuring its plugged in and on

        foreach c: item:
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
                
        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine after loading the clothes

#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            # Place all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                achieve inside(c, washing_machine)

        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine is closed before starting

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Turn on the washing machine to wash clothes

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Ensure the clothing is placed inside the washing machine

behavior start_wash(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        assert is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Ensure it is a washing machine

        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach c: item:
            if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)
        # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine

        start_wash(washing_machine)
        # Start the wash cycle

#goal_representation
 
def has_clothes_in_basket(basket: item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in a specified basket
    symbol has_clothes=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return has_clothes

behavior load_washing_machine(c: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(c, washing_machine)
        # Load the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine) # Close the washing machine door
        achieve is_on(washing_machine) # Turn on the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select a washing machine

        if has_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            foreach c: item:
            # Load all clothes from the basket into the washing machine
                if is_clothes(c) and inside(c, basket):
                    load_washing_machine(c, washing_machine)

            start_washing_machine(washing_machine) # Start the washing machine


#goal_representation_end

#goal_representation
 
def is_clothes_in_basket(basket:item):
    # Function to check if there are clothes in the specified basket
    symbol clothes_in_basket=exists o: item : is_clothes(o) and inside(o, basket)
    return clothes_in_basket

behavior load_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Place the clothes inside the washing machine

behavior start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        # Ensure the washing machine door is closed
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)
        # Start the washing machine

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes
        
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine
        
        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)

        start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

behavior load_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes:item, washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)

behavior close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(washing_machine)
        achieve is_on(washing_machine)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine)
        # Select the washing machine

        foreach clothes: item:
            if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                load_clothes_in_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
        close_and_start_washing_machine(washing_machine)

#goal_representation
 
behavior load_washing_machine(clothes: item, washing_machine: item):
    body:
        achieve inside(clothes, washing_machine)
        # Ensure clothes are placed inside the washing machine

def is_clothes_in_basket(clothes: item, basket: item):
    # Define a function to check if clothes are in the basket for clothes
    symbol in_basket=exists item: item : is_clothes(item) and inside(item, basket)
    return in_basket

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind washing_machine: item where:
            is_washing_machine(washing_machine) and plugged(washing_machine) and is_on(washing_machine)
        # Select a washing machine that is plugged in and turned on

        bind basket: item where:
            is_basket_for_clothes(basket)
        # Select the basket for clothes

        if is_clothes_in_basket(basket):
            foreach clothes: item:
                if is_clothes(clothes) and inside(clothes, basket):
                    load_washing_machine(clothes, washing_machine)
